{"tid":1543790,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有關IVE轉校一問","createTime":"2019-09-05T10:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T16:45:47.000Z","uid":26781,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"33e747e2d98c35d13056f526fbf9e74a3612f76c","tid":1543790,"uid":26781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:18:09.000Z","msg":"小弟本身讀緊沙田商業基礎文憑，而家想轉觀塘IVE同一科，主要原因有兩個：<br />\n<br />\n1.當初揀沙田係因為貪佢大同多女，但發覺自己好on9, 根本唔需要care呢啲嘢而令自己路程遠左（自己住樂富）<br />\n<br />\n2. 我知呢一點好幼稚，但我同班人係完全傾唔埋，人地個個本身識落一齊讀，得我自己一個好似邊緣人咁，心理壓力好大所以想轉校博一博（萬一都係咁嘅情況起碼我地點近左，冇乜蝕底）<br />\n<br />\n想問而家仲可唔可以搞轉校？聽日翻早諗住放學後即刻仆過去<br />\n<br />\n想知錢係咪唔需要再交？只要帶齊身分證明文件同學歷證明就OK？<br />\n<br />\n唔好屌我唔自己打去問住，個陣打去問幾時oday都已經hea鳩我，爬文我驚而家個制度同以前會唔同<br />\n<br />\n最後拜託曬各位，萬分感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575cacae02c7dd6d79efb26f3dfde1d165474337","tid":1543790,"uid":136624,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:20:24.000Z","msg":"打過去問 <br />\n完"},{"pid":"7ae09df7323bad9bb99121185fe65b8dc51b3466","tid":1543790,"uid":26781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"575cacae02c7dd6d79efb26f3dfde1d165474337","tid":1543790,"uid":136624,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:20:24.000Z","msg":"打過去問 <br />\n完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:49:29.000Z","msg":"聽日放左學會打去問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想有呢方面經驗嘅巴絲係呢到講下<br />\n做個心理準備"},{"pid":"086f93d815fcc9c35e81e1aec9f33c59f3b4d7bc","tid":1543790,"uid":61922,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:54:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38bed453f2cbdc27f20e6f42eae19d96b94e983b","tid":1543790,"uid":26781,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"086f93d815fcc9c35e81e1aec9f33c59f3b4d7bc","tid":1543790,"uid":61922,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,